snippet.title: The Equalizer 4 (2026) – First Trailer | Denzel Washington, Keanu Reeves | Concept Trailer
snippet.description:
#theequalizer4 #denzelwashington #jasonstatham #keanureeves 
Watch the first look at The Equalizer 4 (2026) — a powerful fan-made concept trailer imagining the return of Denzel Washington as Robert McCall, joined by Keanu Reeves in a thrilling crossover of two legendary action worlds.

This concept envisions a darker, high-stakes continuation where McCall faces a global syndicate that pushes his moral code to the edge. When his mission collides with a mysterious ex-assassin (played by Keanu Reeves), the result is an explosive alliance of justice and vengeance.

While The Equalizer 4 has not been officially confirmed by Sony or Antoine Fuqua, this fan-made trailer brings to life the kind of intense, cinematic action fans dream of seeing from two of Hollywood’s greatest icons.

snippet.title: Minecraft Speedrunner Swap VS 2 Hunters
snippet.description:
This was crazy intense. Manhunt, but with a twist.

This video, I teamed up with a Manhunt NOOB, Dr Donut, in a new #MinecraftManhunt challenge. We have to speedrun and beat Minecraft against two hunters, but we swap who is playing every minute! It was hilarious and super intense.

Follow my socials:
➽ Twitter - @dreamwastaken
➽ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
➽ Snapchat - @dreampublic


In this challenge Dr Donut and I essentially are one player. We share an inventory, health, position, and basically everything else. The idea is that we are swapping who has control of one player. When we are swapped out, we don't know what is happening at all. We see a black screen and hear nothing.

This is one of my first ever collabs of this type, if you'd like to see more, like the video!

This was played on Minecraft 1.21.8, and is a custom coded challenge. There were a few bugs that we plan to iron out before we try something like this again!

200,000 likes for me to try this challenge with someone else!


DrDonut: @DrDonutt 
Skeppy: @Skeppy 
Daquavis: @DaquavisMC 

Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/DreamWasTaken
